Third Lora Release, 加賀 - Kaga Azur Lane, Like Akagi i didn't see a Kaga Lora or much IA Art, so i created one again.

items.name: Back Wings
items.description:
Most models will draw the wings behind the character regardless of the direction they are facing. This LoRA is designed to put the wings on their back even when the back is towards the viewer.

This is a UNet-only training, so it should work with the same prompts you would normally use. It is trained against an anime model, so you should use Danbooru-style tagging to prompt it, such as "wings, from behind". There were some NSFW images in the training set, but it should work for both NSFW and SFW purposes.

modelVersions.name: LOCON-Light
modelVersions.description: This is from an earlier epoch of the regular LOCON version, so it has a much smaller effect on style, but is less reliable at getting a good pair of wings. The recommended way to use these is to generate an initial image with the regular LOCON to get a nice initial wing shape, then do a 2x upscale in img2img at 0.5 denoise using this one so that the wings will stay on the subject's back without affecting the style of the base model. You can also do 0.5 weight on this and 0.5 weight on the regular version or some other ratio to find the right balance.

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description: Reduced the alpha value to create a smaller file and updated to use some new training options, setting min SNR gamma to 5 and only training the down side of the UNet, which should should further reduce the file size and affect the style of the base model less, as it only changes the first few steps to get the wings in the correct place.

modelVersions.name: LOCON
modelVersions.description: LOCON version. This has a stronger effect on style than v2, but is much more reliable about getting the wings where they are supposed to be and should have less effect on style than v1.

items.name: Yuxiangrousi 鱼香肉丝
items.description:
这款Lora模型专门用于绘制鱼香肉丝这道菜。我意识到在英语中，很难找到一个准确的词汇来描述鱼香肉丝，Sliced Pork, Shredded Pork都不是中式肉丝的切法，更别提炒出来的感觉了，最初的训练图里也就没人打过这种标签。既然无法用英语精确表达，我们就直接使用原名。通过输入“Yuxiangrousi”或“Yuxiang Shredded Pork”，均可激活此功能。该模型基于SD1.5训练，因此应该可以与其他基于SD1.5的模型混用。

This Lora model is specifically designed for drawing the Chinese dish Yuxiangrousi, also known as Yuxiang Shredded Pork. I realized that it's difficult to find an accurate English term to describe this dish, particularly the Chinese-style shredded pork. Since there isn't a precise translation, we can use the original names directly. By inputting either "Yuxiangrousi" or "Yuxiang Shredded Pork," the function can be triggered. The model is based on SD1.5 training, so it should be compatible with other SD1.5-based models.

このLoraモデルは、魚香肉絲（ユーシャンロウスー）として知られる中国料理を描くために特別に設計されています。英語では、特に中国風の細切れ豚肉を表す正確な言葉が見つけにくいことに気づきました。正確な翻訳がないので、元の名前をそのまま使用できます。 「Yuxiangrousi」または「Yuxiang Shredded Pork」と入力すると、機能がトリガーされます。このモデルはSD1.5トレーニングに基づいており、他のSD1.5ベースのモデルと互換性があるはずです。

items.name: Sayla Mass (Gundam) LoRA
items.description:
The M stands for Massive!

General Info

This LoRA for one of the most classic and iconic characters in the Gundam history has been brought to you through training with the Anything v4.5 model. It allows for a variety of styles and settings depending on your prompt and the model you use. The compatibility with semi-realistic models can be quite impressive and let you create pictures with that classic gundam feel to them.

Usage

The model has been trained using Kohya so you probably want to use it in the same way as you use other Kohya models. If you are Using A1111's Webui you want to move the file into the models>Lora directory. It is very important to use the relevant trigger word so that you can get results that look close to mine or even better. I advise using a weight of 0.6-1.0 but you might even be able to go lower in some cases.

Some of the special and interesting aspects of the movie include:

  1. The dynamic between Léon and Mathilda: The movie focuses heavily on the unique and complicated relationship between Léon, who is emotionally detached and a skilled assassin, and Mathilda, who is a young girl seeking refuge after her family is killed. As they spend more time together, they form a deep bond that challenges the boundaries of what is considered socially acceptable.

  2. The themes of morality and redemption: The movie explores themes of morality and redemption through the character of Léon, who begins to question the violent life he leads after forming a bond with Mathilda. This leads him to make choices that ultimately have significant consequences for both him and Mathilda.

  3. The intense action sequences: The movie also features intense action sequences, including some of the most memorable shootouts in cinematic history. These scenes add to the tension and drama of the movie and contribute to its reputation as a classic thriller.

  4. The performances of the actors: The movie features outstanding performances from the entire cast, including Jean Reno, Natalie Portman, and Gary Oldman, who plays the villainous DEA agent Stansfield. The actors bring depth and nuance to their roles and help to make the movie a standout in the thriller genre.

items.name: Khyle. Style Definitive [72MB]
items.description:
This is a LoRA of the Amazing artist Khyle.

Go check him out on patreon to get the content from the source https://www.patreon.com/khyleri

This LoRA was trained on Anything v4.0 and contained 170 Images in the Dataset.

Weightings can range from 0.5 to 0.9, its very versatile and the art style will stick with it the whole way, was well as the shenanigans and dynamic scenes that makes Khyle. so popular.

No tags are required for this LoRA, however if you wish to get things to look more like the source try using the below tags:

warm lighting, film grain, and blurry (or blurry background)

There are some baked in characters such as Ryuko Matoi, Power, Kobeni, Aqua (Face), Nagatoro, Yor, and Anya.

Can easily get NSFW, although its very much an impression of what Khyle's NSFW would look like because he has only used nudity on small number of occasions.

I previously uploaded a 9MB lora series of Khyle. and it was actually some of my first LoRAs I created. Considering it happened to be my favourite, I had to give it a go with more gusto this time.

Hope you have as much fun as I have had with it.




If you have any LoRA requests and wouldnt mind buying me a Hot Chocolate, please consider going to my page. https://www.buymeacoffee.com/JohnStinko
